---
import SiteLayout from '~/layouts/SiteLayout.astro';
import Container from '~/components/site/Container.astro';

const metadata = {
  title: 'About Us',
  description:
    'Learn how Ecolog Solutions delivers reliable commercial cleaning with clear checklists, consistent teams, and proactive communication.',
};
---

<SiteLayout metadata={metadata}>
  <section class="bg-page dark:bg-slate-950">
    <Container class="py-14 sm:py-20">
      <p class="text-base sm:text-lg font-semibold text-primary dark:text-accent">About us</p>
      <h1 class="mt-3 text-4xl font-bold tracking-tight text-gray-900 dark:text-white sm:text-5xl">
        We're built for <span class="text-primary dark:text-accent">consistency</span>
      </h1>
      <p class="mt-4 max-w-3xl text-base leading-7 text-muted sm:text-lg">
        Commercial cleaning works best when it is predictable. Our goal is simple: keep facilities
        <span class="text-white dark:text-white font-semibold"> clean</span>,
        <span class="text-white dark:text-white font-semibold"> safe</span>, and
        <span class="text-white dark:text-white font-semibold"> ready</span> for customers and staff, without surprises.
      </p>

      <div class="mt-12 grid gap-8 lg:grid-cols-12">
        <div class="lg:col-span-7">
          <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold tracking-tight text-white dark:text-white sm:text-4xl">
            What clients can expect
          </h2>
          <div class="mt-6 grid gap-6 sm:grid-cols-2">
            <div
              class="rounded-2xl border border-primary bg-white p-6 shadow-sm dark:border-primary/60 dark:bg-slate-950"
            >
              <h3 class="text-base font-semibold text-gray-900 dark:text-white">Clear scope</h3>
              <p class="mt-2 text-sm text-muted">
                A checklist defines tasks and frequency, so results match expectations.
              </p>
            </div>
            <div
              class="rounded-2xl border border-primary bg-white p-6 shadow-sm dark:border-primary/60 dark:bg-slate-950"
            >
              <h3 class="text-base font-semibold text-gray-900 dark:text-white">Proactive communication</h3>
              <p class="mt-2 text-sm text-muted">Fast updates when needs change, with simple escalation paths.</p>
            </div>
            <div
              class="rounded-2xl border border-primary bg-white p-6 shadow-sm dark:border-primary/60 dark:bg-slate-950"
            >
              <h3 class="text-base font-semibold text-gray-900 dark:text-white">Reliable crews</h3>
              <p class="mt-2 text-sm text-muted">Consistent staffing wherever possible to build trust and routine.</p>
            </div>
            <div
              class="rounded-2xl border border-primary bg-white p-6 shadow-sm dark:border-primary/60 dark:bg-slate-950"
            >
              <h3 class="text-base font-semibold text-gray-900 dark:text-white">Quality checks</h3>
              <p class="mt-2 text-sm text-muted">Periodic spot checks and feedback loops to keep standards high.</p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <aside class="lg:col-span-5 flex lg:pt-14">
          <div
            class="h-full w-full overflow-hidden rounded-3xl border border-primary bg-white shadow-sm dark:border-primary/60 dark:bg-slate-950"
          >
            <img
              src="/ecolog10.png"
              alt="Ecolog team at work"
              class="block h-full w-full object-cover"
              loading="lazy"
            />
          </div>
        </aside>
      </div>

      <div class="mt-10 space-y-3">
        <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold tracking-tight text-white dark:text-white sm:text-4xl">Our story</h2>
        <p class="w-full text-sm text-muted sm:text-base">
          Ecolog started as a small crew focused on dependable cleaning and clear checklists. Over the years, we grew by
          earning trust: adding trained teams, safety programs, and specialized services that support regulated
          facilities. Today, our legacy is built on consistency: the same care for people, predictable results for
          clients, and a culture that keeps improving with every site we serve. We invest in training, safety, and the
          right tools so every team member can do their best work. We also keep communication simple and proactive, so
          clients always know what to expect and when. That partnership mindset is how we continue to grow, along with
          reliable people, steady results, and a commitment to doing the job right.
        </p>
      </div>
    </Container>
  </section>
</SiteLayout>
